 <t t-set="template" t-value="object.get_report_template()"/>
                <div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">
                    <t t-if="template">
                        <p t-if="template == 5"
                           style="margin:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
                            <i>
                                <font style="font-size:12px;">
                                    If you have any questions regarding the organization of your project, please do not
                                    reply to this e-mail and contact the
                                    project manager directly via the link
                                </font>
                                <a style="text-decoration:none;background-color:transparent;color:rgb(0, 135, 132);"
                                   t-attf-href="{{ object.sale_order_id.get_portal_url() }} ">
                                    <font style="font-size:12px;"><t t-out="object.sale_order_id.name">SO12345</t>.
                                    </font>
                                </a>
                            </i>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>

                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                            Dear <t t-out="object.partner_id.display_name or '''client'''"></t>,
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>

                        <p t-if="template == 1" style="margin:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
                            Please find attached the invoice <strong><t t-out="object.name">FAC/2024/123</t></strong>
                            for an amount of <strong><t t-out="format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id)">50.00 €</t></strong>
                            related to the intervention <strong><t t-out="object.sale_order_id.name">SOXXX</t></strong>.
                            <br/>
                            The invoice must be paid to the account <strong><t t-out="object.partner_bank_id.display_name  or 'Belfius - BE86 0689 4661 5650'">[Recipient bank account]</t></strong> using the following reference: <strong><t t-out="object.name">FAC/2024/123</t></strong>.
                            <br/>
                            We kindly thank you in advance for ensuring payment before the due date on <strong><t t-out="object.invoice_date_due.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')">dd/mm/yyyy</t></strong>.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>

                        <p t-elif="template == 5"
                           style="margin:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
                            Please find enclosed the down-payment invoice
                            <strong>
                                <t t-out="object.name">FAC/2024/123</t>
                            </strong>
                            for
                            <strong>
                                <t t-out="format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id)">50,00 €</t>
                            </strong>
                            .
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            We thank you in advance for paying the invoice as soon as possible so that we can organize the project quickly.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            If this is an urgent job, please return the proof of payment in reply to this e-mail.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>

                        <p t-elif="template == 6"
                           style="margin:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
                            Please find enclosed the credit note
                            <strong>
                                <t t-out="object.name">NC/2024/123</t>
                            </strong>
                            in the amount of
                            <strong>
                                <t t-out="format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id)">50,00 €</t>
                            </strong>
                            .
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            You can deduct this amount from your next payment, or tell us which on which bank account number you wish to be reimbursed by replying to this e-mail.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>
                    </t>
                    <t t-else="">
                        <p style="margin:0px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;padding:0px;font-size: 13px;">
                            Dear
                            <t t-if="object.partner_id.parent_id">
                                <t t-out="object.partner_id.name"></t>
                                (<t t-out="object.partner_id.parent_id.name"></t>),
                            </t>
                            <t t-else="">
                                <t t-out="object.partner_id.name"></t>,
                            </t>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            Here is your
                            <t t-if="object.name">
                                invoice
                                <strong>
                                    <t t-out="object.name">FAC/2024/123</t>
                                </strong>
                            </t>
                            <t t-else="">
                                invoice
                            </t>
                            <t t-if="object.invoice_origin">
                                (with reference: <t t-out="object.invoice_origin">ref invoice</t>)
                            </t>
                            for
                            <strong>
                                <t t-out="format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id)">50,00 €</t>
                            </strong>
                            from <t t-out="object.company_id.name">Heat Me</t>.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            We thank you in advance for taking care of its payment.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                        </p>
                    </t>

                    <div id="qrcode" t-if="object.display_qr_code and object.amount_residual > 0">
                        <t t-set="qr_code_url" t-value="object._generate_qr_code(silent_errors=True)"/>
                        <p t-if="qr_code_url">
                            <strong class="text-center">Scan me with your banking app.</strong><br/><br/>
                            <img class="border border-dark rounded" t-att-src="qr_code_url"/>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <p style="margin:0px;font-size:13px;font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
                        Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions.
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        Kind regards,
                        <br/>
                        The accounting department
                    </p>
                </div>